I receive a lot of questions regarding Turo's Trip Fees.  This is a variable fee,  based on several factors mainly how many days the initial trip is and how far in advance it is booked.  
 Try booking the trip with more advance notice, And then you can normally change your start time to pick it up sooner.... this method should help keep the trip fees lower. Also, the longer the Initial trip is, the lower the daily trip fee will be for the duration of your trip.
